Summary: Saw black object , no sound, no lights, changing to different shapes
divs: Sighting DetailsWe saw a dark object coming towards us then moving away traveling south to north. Approximatly 3000 to 6000 feet above the ground. There were no lights or sound as it went past us. It was changing shapes, difficult to decribe. Definitly not an airplane. One of us is a commercial pilot 53 years old with 28 years of flying experience and has never seen anything like this.
